    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Ok I have badly expressed this widget. I wanted to express a list where you can select only one item.\n\nBut this is exactly what a menu is. The \"type\" of the instant search demo (please look at the demo or screenshot in the description) IS a menu. Then we could either hide or show the values that are not selected.\n\nI propose for this use case to expose the `widgets.menu`.\n\n@redox We had a good chat with @bobylito about how to implement the \"type\" list fomr the instant seearch demo (see the screenshot or the demo). And what we do here is constructing a menu where you can select one of the item.\n\nSo I am closing this.\n",
